0 Y0 K40<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>TRIPLE colours in Pantone<\/td><td>YELLOW: 137C<br>RED: 185C<br>PURPLE: 2622C<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>TRIPLE colours in Hex<\/td><td>YELLOW: #FBB040<br>RED: #ED1C24<br>PURPLE: #622166<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>TRIPLE colours in Gray<\/td><td>Black 100%, 70% , 30%<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>TRIPLE Presentation Template<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:25% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/TRIPLE-presentation-template_firstslide-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-524 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/TRIPLE-presentation-template_firstslide-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/TRIPLE-presentation-template_firstslide-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/TRIPLE-presentation-template_firstslide-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/TRIPLE-presentation-template_firstslide.png 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">Download the template for TRIPLE PowerPoint presentations (pptx, version Sept. 2021) here: <a href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/TRIPLE_PPT_TEMPLATE_2021_09_03.pptx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">TRIPLE presentation <\/a><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Contact us at triple[at]operas-eu.org if you need a *.potx file of the TRIPLE presentation template.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20